# ─── BYOK CUSTOM PATCH: mobile bridge static bundle (Patch 50) ─────────
# Preserved by .github/scripts/apply-byok-patches.sh. Do not remove.
# The Vite-built mobile UI is force-added under src/extension/byokRemote/
# dist/ (past the upstream blanket dist/ rule in .gitignore). Without this
# allow rule, vsce strips it from the VSIX and the bridgeServer has
# nothing to serve.
